    "text": "No Taxpayer Funded Platform for Chinese Communists Act\n\nThis bill prohibits using federal funds made available to the U.S. Agency for Global Media to provide an open platform for representatives of the Chinese government, the Chinese Communist Party (CCP), or any entity owned or controlled by the Chinese government or by the CCP."
